<varlistentry id="options.SeparateButtonTitle">
	<term>SeparateButtonTitle <emphasis remap='I'>0|1</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies  where  iconified  window  titles should be drawn.  If
              it is 0, the title will be drawn at the top of the icon.   If
              it  is 1, the title will be drawn in a separate window at the
              below the icon.  The default value  is 1.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
